snippet: The agency said it received a record number of applicants for its next astronaut class.
abstract: NASA announces record number of people have applied for next astronaut class, with around 18,300 applications received for some 8 to 14 potential openings.
lead_paragraph: The agency said it received a record number of applicants for its next astronaut class.
